name: CSDT\CSR4\ConfidenceInterface
long_desc: This interface is used to define the confidence levels of the mapper support

UNSUPPORTED_CONFIDENCE.name: UNSUPPORTED_CONFIDENCE
UNSUPPORTED_CONFIDENCE.long_desc: This constant is used to represent a unsupported confidence level

LOW_CONFIDENCE.name: LOW_CONFIDENCE
LOW_CONFIDENCE.long_desc: This constant is used to represent a low confidence level of support

MEDIUM_CONFIDENCE.name: MEDIUM_CONFIDENCE
MEDIUM_CONFIDENCE.long_desc: This constant is used to represent a medium confidence level of support

HIGH_CONFIDENCE.name: HIGH_CONFIDENCE
HIGH_CONFIDENCE.long_desc: This constant is used to represent a high confidence level of support

DEDICATED_CONFIDENCE.name: DEDICATED_CONFIDENCE
DEDICATED_CONFIDENCE.long_desc: This constant is used to represent a dedicated level of support
